Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:34.52,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,For us to return to \Nbeing ordinary humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:38.01,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,it is necessary for you to regain \Nyour Soul Reaper powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:55.60,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not the answer I want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:56.72,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:02.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what’s happening \Nto me and my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:07.60,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Whether I regain my Soul \NReaper powers or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:09.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,is beside the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.65,0:02:31.21,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,You’re okay with letting \Nhim leave like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.50,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:36.69,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,We told him out of the blue to \Nbecome a Soul Reaper again—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:38.67,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,an immediate answer would \Nbe asking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:43.22,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,You of all people should understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:48.56,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Becoming a Soul Reaper again \Nwas never on his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.60,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,But he thought we might know something
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:57.53,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,regarding the incidents that suddenly \Nbegan happening around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:00.90,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, he decided to approach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.04,0:03:04.89,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve made great progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:08.87,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t afford to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.33,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t let this chance slip by.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.38,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:21.35,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think that guy \Nis worth all the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:22.85,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.79,0:03:27.49,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,wanting to restore his powers \Nfor your personal reasons
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.49,0:03:32.35,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,and whether he can actually be of \Nhelp to us are two different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:38.53,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, it seems like some of \Nus are already interested in him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:41.99,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,so in that regard, I might \Nbe different from you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.23,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:44.94,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What, were you referring to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.66,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,She didn’t say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:51.61,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think he’s \Nworth all the risk either!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:54.26,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,But we do need his powers, don’t we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:57.52,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,So says the one who is all hyper \Nafter seeing him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:03:59.45,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Shush!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:00.85,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m always hyper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.15,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:04.68,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do you guys think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.92,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Yukio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:07.35,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t care…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:12.35,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t care? And you, Giriko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.89,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s clear that…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:18.02,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,we do need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:49.07,B2,MALE,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.81,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, good…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.70,0:04:58.02,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Reapers haven’t \Nfound you yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.04,0:05:02.28,B2,MALE,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell…are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:07.16,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,It must be agonizing to \Ncarry such a grudge…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:10.67,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,I will free you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.66,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:24.09,B2,TSUKISHIMA,0000,0000,0000,,Will you do as I ask? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.51,B2,STUDENT,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:40.17,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,I came because you asked me \Nto, but what is all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:41.11,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:43.94,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Not so loud! He’ll hear us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:47.20,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going to confirm with \Nour own eyes whether or not
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.24,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,that guy is really somebody we need!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.89,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,You’re totally into this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:53.76,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:54.98,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,He’ll hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:06:00.65,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,He turned the corner. Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.00,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.19,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,Count me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:10.82,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.64,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Hi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:18.10,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.74,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see how you’re doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:24.93,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:27.15,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you’ve got a lot \Nof free time in the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:32.11,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,so I chose some DVD’s \Nfeaturing young entertainers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:34.97,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,who might have a breakout \Nin another two years…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:38.34,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…Thanks…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:39.87,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,How’re you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.22,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m doing good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.05,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,It still hurts, though…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:48.80,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,If it’s that bad, shall I heal you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.62,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, but that’s okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:54.24,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,I have my reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:01.62,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,So? You didn’t come just \Nto see how I was, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:06.22,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,When they found you collapsed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:09.36,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,you weren’t very far from \NKurosaki’s home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:13.53,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering why you were there…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.79,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Could it have been because,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:21.29,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,like me, you sensed something \Ngoing on around Kurosaki, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.87,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.14,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s true that I did sense
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:28.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,some kind of Spiritual \NPressure around Kurosaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:31.45,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,but it had nothing to do with \Nthe guy who attacked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:32.91,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:33.63,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:34.80,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:38.27,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Was that a?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.31,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a Hollow! And it’s nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.61,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn’t, Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.54,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll go and take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:45.90,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,You, Inoue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.15,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.15,0:07:48.89,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t do anything dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:49.86,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.43,B2,ISHIDA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:59.83,B2,ISHIDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She’s right, a Hollow like \Nthis should be no problem…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.33,B2,ISHIDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.25,B2,ISHIDA (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what worries me is…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:27.86,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,He startled me! Why’d he suddenly…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.26,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this presence I feel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:35.78,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:37.45,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:40.33,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong? Why’re \Nyou so flustered?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:41.33,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.92,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:45.82,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a Hollow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:52.25,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.25,0:08:54.42,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Must’ve been my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:56.16,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Is it always like this for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:57.53,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.72,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,I usually let Ishida and \NSado take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.12,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.12,0:09:03.18,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:07.23,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what were you \Ndoing here, Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.27,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:11.20,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,-But what about you, Inoue?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.59,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,-Who is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.15,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,-Huh, me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:15.45,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for walking me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.19,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:18.46,B2,ORIHIME,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:35.09,B2,ICHIGO (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don’t like clinging to the past…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:54.39,B2,GINJO (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you’re saying you don’t \Nwant your Soul Reaper powers?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:34.28,B2,GINJO (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’m not asking for \Nan immediate answer.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.86,B2,GINJO (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’ll wait until tomorrow \Nfor your reply.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:40.03,B2,GINJO (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think it over tonight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:41.42,B2,ICHIGO (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:49.04,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It’s true that the way I am \Nnow, I can’t protect anyone…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:53.42,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I did it knowing the consequences.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:11:00.33,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Yuzu, Brother Ichi says \Nhe doesn’t want dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.84,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.61,0:11:05.02,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Geez…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:08.31,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,And here you prepared his favorites.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.77,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t care anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:15.23,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,I think I’ll go and take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:49.27,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,It appears he won’t be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.79,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you figured wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:12:01.32,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Won’t it become more difficult \Nthe more you insist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:17.38,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Here. You get to eat what you \Ndidn’t have yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.36,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.55,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Brother Ichi…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:25.80,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,Were you expecting someone last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.44,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.43,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:33.41,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,I felt someone was in front \Nof the house, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:36.23,B2,KARIN,0000,0000,0000,,When I went outside, \Nthere was no one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.61,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.74,0:12:42.88,B2,GINJO (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’ll wait until tomorrow \Nfor your reply.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:45.95,B2,GINJO (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think it over tonight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:56.88,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Chad…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.31,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.63,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance, were you \Nat my place last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.14,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,No…I didn’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:06.84,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess it was him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.67,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:12.76,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:18.23,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,What about school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:21.44,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You haven’t been coming \Nat all lately…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:24.99,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember…the promise \Nwe made in middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:30.91,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, you protected something \Nvery important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:34.42,B2,ICHIGO (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you’re going to stake \Nyour life to protect it,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then I’ll stake my \Nlife to protect it, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.24,0:13:39.88,B2,ICHIGO (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It’s a promise.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:47.26,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,From that day on, you and \NI have fought together,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.58,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,and I’ve continued to \Nfollow you in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:54.47,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:57.61,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,You might be trying to hide it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:13:59.64,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,but to tell you the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:02.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s been unbearable to watch \Nyou since you lost your powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.10,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,I know you want to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.02,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,It’s agonizing to be unable to
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.02,0:14:10.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,protect everyone with your \Nown powers, isn’t it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.43,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to hide it, Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:19.00,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Those feelings are who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:26.63,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:29.19,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll be late for class…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:38.14,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,So, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.49,0:14:41.83,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,There really isn’t \Nanything we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:44.98,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,I went to see him, but he \Ngave me no indication…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:46.78,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Ginjo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:50.58,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t you meet \Nwith Ichigo last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:52.78,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.29,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,You went to Ichigo’s \Nplace, didn’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.16,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.21,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,I never went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.61,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.46,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Then who…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:05.56,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:10.18,B2,CHAD,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo’s younger sister sensed the \Npresence of someone around their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.68,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,It’s simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.02,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:20.32,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,Could it mean that someone besides us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:24.94,B2,KUTSUZAWA,0000,0000,0000,,is trying to make \Ncontact with Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.23,B2,VOICES,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:33.98,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.53,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I might’ve sensed…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:37.95,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,A strange presence near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:04.15,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It’s him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:05.48,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:13.19,B2,KARIN (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By the way, Brother Ichi…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:17.49,B2,KARIN (FLASHBACK),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Were you expecting someone last night?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.35,0:16:19.61,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,Could that have been!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.46,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.12,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:54.50,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:56.53,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.27,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:01.00,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:03.96,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,You’re all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.63,0:17:05.67,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:08.08,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…it’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.84,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,I was just on my way
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.67,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,to buy groceries for \Ntonight’s dinner—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.42,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,would you come with me \Nto carry the packages?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:16.02,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Sure…I don’t mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.84,0:17:22.02,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,What was that breeze just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:36.54,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:39.87,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:40.75,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.58,0:17:42.60,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:48.82,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Brother…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:50.29,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Something’s pulling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:51.40,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.38,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It’s a Hollow…no doubt about it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:59.40,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Let Yuzu…go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.26,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Bro…ther…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:09.15,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.40,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Why can’t I see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:12.74,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Bro…ther…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:13.90,B2,YUZU,0000,0000,0000,,Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:16.42,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:19.95,B2,ICHIGO (M),0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.37,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:41.97,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:57.03,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,That hurt, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.32,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Ginjo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:00.72,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,You hung in there well…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:04.16,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go for some ramen noodles,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:07.16,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,after I take care of this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.79,0:19:24.01,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...why’d you \Ngo after this girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.50,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:49.36,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:51.37,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:55.13,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.52,0:20:02.38,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you…big time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.14,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Hell with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.61,0:20:08.19,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t come to make \Nyou indebted to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:12.55,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,We can’t afford to have you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:16.61,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,And besides…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.22,0:20:20.70,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,It sucks to have the door \Nslammed shut on us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.70,0:20:23.03,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,because we didn’t protect something \Nwe could have protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:34.21,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.15,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.17,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You saved him and just came back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:40.13,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,If we need Ichigo Kurosaki’s powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:44.64,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,why didn’t you tell him, “I’ll save you \Nif you cooperate with us” and make a deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:48.98,B2,YUKIO,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you’re all for \Nwelcoming Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:50.14,B2,JACKIE,0000,0000,0000,,Sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:51.31,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,No, I’m not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:54.87,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not getting why you’re \Nhanging everything
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:57.35,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,on that tacky guy with orange hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:59.76,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not tacky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.35,0:21:04.74,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:08.22,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Is your sister okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:09.17,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:12.00,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:15.42,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:16.92,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:19.79,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn’t come because I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.37,0:21:24.70,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I want my powers back so \NI can protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:27.05,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:32.02,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,You still won’t admit it, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:39.06,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,This is…my…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:42.70,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the symbol \Nof your power, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.70,0:21:43.99,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:47.30,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.35,0:23:22.69,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,No one told me he’d be joining us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.69,0:23:25.09,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,What? Stop picking on me just \Nbecause you’re happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:27.51,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,No one said I’m happy or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:28.33,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Or that he’s my type…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:30.39,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Or that he has a sexy voice… \NOr that he has a cute smile…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:31.89,B2,RIRUKA,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not thinking any of that, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.89,0:23:34.85,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,You just explained it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:38.54,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t toss that away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.54,0:23:39.40,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,I won’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.40,0:23:41.53,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,But where’d you find this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:43.48,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:46.48,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,I looked where the river flowed,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.83,0:23:49.24,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,followed the Kuroshio Current
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:51.70,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,and set out on the vast open ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.35,0:23:54.22,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,through stormy seas
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.85,0:23:57.20,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,until at last, on a southern island,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.51,0:23:59.27,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.59,0:24:02.84,B2,GINJO,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t toss that away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.84,0:24:04.66,B2,ICHIGO,0000,0000,0000,,Stop lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:06.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,